# Project Structure & Tech Stack

## Core Philosophy
- **Architecture:** Hybrid JAMstack.
  - **Frontend:** Pre-built Static Files (Vite -> `dist/`).
  - **Backend:** Node.js Express Service (for Admin/Uploads) + Supabase (DB/Auth).
- **Theme:** "Kawaii Pixel Art" (16-bit aesthetic).

